{
  "stem": "1753.6",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And over the years, periodically, I get sort of caught in relating my story.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the early years, I started, and then I stopped, because what we have to say sounds so unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We don't want to be accused of being liars.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At first, we didn't want to know about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were busy earning a living, raising families and so on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But only now in our-- the evening of our lives, we feel it is important to record it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Proof, I never felt I had to prove anything, because it is a-- it's documented and a foregone conclusion.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in fact, there is proof in more than one way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were a  total of nine survivors of which at least seven are still alive.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I'm continuously in touch with them-- some in Israel, some in-- in-- in-- there's one in Miami that know me from there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There is one in Paris that know me from there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We get together periodically, allow me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in 1980, when there was a world gathering of Holocaust survivors in Israel, I took it up on myself and through research, and letters, and communications, I organized, sponsored, and hosted a gathering within the gathering of the Holocaust survivors.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was able to round up from throughout the world each and every one then nine Treblinka survivors.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I hosted a big party only for those survivors at the Tel Aviv Hilton at the King Solomon's Terrace Restaurant.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was recorded by the publications.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we've got one right now, the And we get together periodically, we Treblinka survivors.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there is plenty of material on it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No published list-- only the list that we survivors compiled ourselves.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
